data.meta_description: 11909949_final Report (1) - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document is a training report submitted by Nilesh Yadav to Lovely Professional University in partial fulfillment of the requirements for a Bachelor of Technology degree in Computer Science. It summarizes Nilesh Yadav's internship experience from January 2023 to June 2023 at Xperi Inc., where he worked on the Streamer QE team under the supervision of VasanthRaj Rajanna. The report includes sections on the introduction of the company, the project undertaken, work done, challenges faced and how they were tackled, learning outcomes, and conclusions.
